---
title: Chermoula Lamb Kofta Couscous Bowl with Mint, Yoghurt Drizzle & Feta
description: Spiced lamb koftas steal the show in this vibrant couscous bowl, packed with peppery radish, fragrant mint, and a cooling drizzle of creamy yoghurt. It’s a perfect mix of herby and refreshing flavours.

